The evidence with the title 'Mosque near ground zero stirs mixed feelings for local muslims ... ' says Aug 19, 2010  ... Muslim New Yorkers are grappling deeply with the lingering ambiguities of their place in American society nine years after 9/11 .  ... Anger and accusation over an Islamic center and mosque planned near ground zero , one thing seems clear to Laique Khan : His fellow Muslims have a right to build the project. 
